title: 78. The Equation Of Happiness
itunes:title: 78. The Equation Of Happiness
description: Everybody wants to be happy; unfortunately, not everybody knows what creates happiness. There's no secret, and it does not just come and go from time to time. On today's episode, Andy shares the equation you must understand if you want to create happiness for yourself.
